<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> 26-09-2025</p>

<p><strong>Link Roadways Group</strong> (“we,” “our,” “us”) respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your data.</p>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
<p>We collect only the information necessary to provide app services:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Account Information</strong><br>Email address and password you provide to sign in.</li>
    <li><strong>Camera & Photos</strong><br>To capture or upload images/documents.</li>
    <li><strong>Contacts (Optional)</strong><br>Access only when you choose to share a document via WhatsApp Business Cloud API.</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>We use your data only to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Allow you to sign in with email & password.</li>
    <li>Upload or pick images/documents.</li>
    <li>Share files through WhatsApp Business Cloud API.</li>
    <li>Provide support and improve the app.</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Sharing of Information</h2>
<p>We do not sell your data. We may share only:</p>
<ul>
    <li>With service providers (e.g., hosting or WhatsApp API) to run the app.</li>
    <li>When required by law.</li>
    <li>With your consent for sharing files.</li>
</ul>

<h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
<p>We keep your account and uploaded files only as long as needed for app functionality or as required by law.</p>

<h2>5. Data Security</h2>
<p>We use reasonable measures to safeguard your data from unauthorized access or misuse.</p>

<h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
<p>You may:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Update or delete your account by contacting support.</li>
    <li>Revoke camera or contacts permissions anytime from device settings.</li>
</ul>

<h2>7. Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>The app integrates with WhatsApp Business Cloud API only for document sharing. Their privacy policy applies.</p>

<h2>8. Children’s Privacy</h2>
<p>Link Roadways Group is not for children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect their data.</p>

<h2>9. Changes</h2>
<p>We may update this policy and will notify you in the app or on our website.</p>

<h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
<p>For questions about this Privacy Policy:</p>
<ul>
    <h3>Link Roadways Private Limited</h3>
    <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@linkroadways.in"> info@linkroadways.in</a></li>
    <li><strong>Address:</strong> 254, Ultra Modern Apple Market, Pinjore, Distt. Panchkula - 134 101 (Haryana) INDIA</li>
</ul>


